translation: Defeat the enemy soldiers!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the enemy soldiers!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Destroy all the cannons!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Destroy all the cannons!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Head for the Shrine of Seas.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Head for the Shrine of Seas.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Destroy the Battleship!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Destroy the Battleship!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Are you okay, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Are you okay, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Yeah, I'm fine.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yeah, I'm fine.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: These soldier maggots just piss me off, is all.{#Name="Zero"}
source: These soldier maggots just piss me off, is all.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Maggots? Hey, do you like maggots, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Maggots? Hey, do you like maggots, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What kind of question is that? Of course not.{#Name="Zero"}
source: What kind of question is that? Of course not.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh. I thought maybe you had some.{LF}I'm kinda hungry...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh. I thought maybe you had some.{LF}I'm kinda hungry...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Don't eat maggots, dummy!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Don't eat maggots, dummy!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm getting kinda tired...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm getting kinda tired...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Stop whining.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Stop whining.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, flying is pretty hard, okay?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, flying is pretty hard, okay?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Stop complaining.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Stop complaining.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I mean...uh...it's fun! So fun! Wheee!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I mean...uh...it's fun! So fun! Wheee!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You can stop lying, too.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You can stop lying, too.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Dieee!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Dieee!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: That's my line, shitface!{#Name="Zero"}
source: That's my line, shitface!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You're mine, demon! Mine!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: You're mine, demon! Mine!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Shouldn't you be suckling on Mommy's teat right now?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Shouldn't you be suckling on Mommy's teat right now?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You're not coming anywhere near Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: You're not coming anywhere near Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Lady Five, Lady Five!{LF}...Pathetic.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Lady Five, Lady Five!{LF}...Pathetic.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Just die, would you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Just die, would you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'll give you something to cry about!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: I'll give you something to cry about!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Move it, Gramps.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Move it, Gramps.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: ゼロ！ゼロ！また会えたね！{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: ゼロ！ゼロ！また会えたね！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: 臭っ！近寄るな、馬鹿{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 臭っ！近寄るな、馬鹿{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: えっ。ボク臭い？{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: えっ。ボク臭い？{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: 臭いヤツほど自分のにおいに鈍感なんだ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 臭いヤツほど自分のにおいに鈍感なんだ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: Hey, Zero? What do I smell like?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, Zero? What do I smell like?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: A bloated goat carcass stuffed with rotting fish.{#Name="Zero"}
source: A bloated goat carcass stuffed with rotting fish.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh! That...doesn't sound good at all.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh! That...doesn't sound good at all.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Yeah. Now imagine having to ride on that thing.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yeah. Now imagine having to ride on that thing.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Tee hee! I bet it's fun.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Tee hee! I bet it's fun.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I'm sorry I smell like fish...{LF}But we ARE fighting out at sea.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm sorry I smell like fish...{LF}But we ARE fighting out at sea.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You're not screwing around in the water, are you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You're not screwing around in the water, are you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: M-Me!? I, uh...no way! No! No...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: M-Me!? I, uh...no way! No! No...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: If you're lying, I'm gonna kick your ass.{#Name="Zero"}
source: If you're lying, I'm gonna kick your ass.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm sorry...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm sorry...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: また上がってきた！{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: また上がってきた！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: Where are you, Five?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Where are you, Five?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You still haven't sunk that thing yet?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You still haven't sunk that thing yet?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, it's hard, okay? It's a giant battleship!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, it's hard, okay? It's a giant battleship!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Can you help me out, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Can you help me out, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Fine, fine.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Fine, fine.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: キミのその臭い背中にのってやるよ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: キミのその臭い背中にのってやるよ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ありがとう！今度、背中に香水つけとくね{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: ありがとう！今度、背中に香水つけとくね{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: やめろ。臭さが増すだけだ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: やめろ。臭さが増すだけだ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: デカイだけの軍艦なんて物の数じゃない{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: デカイだけの軍艦なんて物の数じゃない{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: がんばってね！{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: がんばってね！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: 一緒に倒すんだよ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 一緒に倒すんだよ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: All right. Let's take care of business.{#Name="Zero"}
source: All right. Let's take care of business.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Right!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Right!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Having you on my back makes me{LF}feel a lot stronger, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Having you on my back makes me{LF}feel a lot stronger, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's your imagination. But you better{LF}get stronger for real soon, or else!{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's your imagination. But you better{LF}get stronger for real soon, or else!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: O-Okay...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: O-Okay...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Just fly where I tell you and shut up, all right?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Just fly where I tell you and shut up, all right?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Okay! Um...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Okay! Um...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Well, I never really learned left from right,{LF}sooo...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Well, I never really learned left from right,{LF}sooo...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You've got to be kidding me.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You've got to be kidding me.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You haven't damaged this thing at all, have you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You haven't damaged this thing at all, have you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I was saving it for you, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I was saving it for you, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: For me?{#Name="Zero"}
source: For me?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Yeah! 'Cause I knew you'd love blowing it up!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Yeah! 'Cause I knew you'd love blowing it up!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Grr...{#Name="Zero"}
source: Grr...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Just my little random act of kindness. Neat, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Just my little random act of kindness. Neat, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Goddammit, dragon!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Goddammit, dragon!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ow, ow, ow! Why'd you just STAB ME!?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Ow, ow, ow! Why'd you just STAB ME!?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Damn. This is tough.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Damn. This is tough.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: SEE!? Battleships are actually super strong!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: SEE!? Battleships are actually super strong!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: They can't be stronger than a dragon.{#Name="Zero"}
source: They can't be stronger than a dragon.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Er...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Er...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Come on! Come on!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Come on! Come on!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You're flying too slow, dummy!{#Name="Zero"}
source: You're flying too slow, dummy!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm trying, Zero! I'm really trying!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm trying, Zero! I'm really trying!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Well, try harder.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Well, try harder.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I want results, not excuses.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I want results, not excuses.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Once we sink this thing, we get to see Five, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Once we sink this thing, we get to see Five, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Yep. Then the real fireworks start.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yep. Then the real fireworks start.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, yay! Fireworks are the best!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh, yay! Fireworks are the best!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Idiot...{#Name="Zero"}
source: Idiot...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Look out!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Look out!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Whew! That was a close one!{LF}Did you see it? Did you?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Whew! That was a close one!{LF}Did you see it? Did you?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: That wasn't CLOSE! It was a direct hit!{#Name="Zero"}
source: That wasn't CLOSE! It was a direct hit!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, I'm trying pretty hard for you, aren't I?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, I'm trying pretty hard for you, aren't I?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's okay to praise me sometimes.{LF}Maybe tell me how good I'm doing?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: It's okay to praise me sometimes.{LF}Maybe tell me how good I'm doing?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Shut up, dumbass!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Shut up, dumbass!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: That's not exactly what I had in mind...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: That's not exactly what I had in mind...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Faster! Higher! Keep flying!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Faster! Higher! Keep flying!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: It's haaaaaard!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: It's haaaaaard!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Hard? A real dragon could do this in his sleep.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hard? A real dragon could do this in his sleep.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, you're comparing me to Michael again,{LF}aren't you?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, you're comparing me to Michael again,{LF}aren't you?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I would never do that.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I would never do that.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Really?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Really?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Yes, really. Because Michael was amazing,{LF}and you're a big dummy.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Yes, really. Because Michael was amazing,{LF}and you're a big dummy.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I wish you'd use my name like you use his...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I wish you'd use my name like you use his...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Well, you just watch. I'm gonna fight real{LF}hard so you HAVE to use my name!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Well, you just watch. I'm gonna fight real{LF}hard so you HAVE to use my name!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: There it is. Five is in that shrine.{#Name="Zero"}
source: There it is. Five is in that shrine.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Her dragon's not with her!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Her dragon's not with her!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Now's our chance to put her in the ground!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Now's our chance to put her in the ground!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Look at her! The Intoner's drenched in blood!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Look at her! The Intoner's drenched in blood!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: The traitor Zero must be eliminated!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: The traitor Zero must be eliminated!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Indeed! It's time to show her the power of our united forces!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Indeed! It's time to show her the power of our united forces!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: I'll kill you... I'll kill you... I'LL KILL YOU!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: I'll kill you... I'll kill you... I'LL KILL YOU!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Calm down, idiot!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Calm down, idiot!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: It pains me to think how frightened Lady Five must be right now...{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: It pains me to think how frightened Lady Five must be right now...{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Don't worry. She's got Dito with her.{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Don't worry. She's got Dito with her.{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: That's why it pains me!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: That's why it pains me!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: How can our Intoner abide him? It makes no sense!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: How can our Intoner abide him? It makes no sense!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Well...this is the end...{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Well...this is the end...{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Don't give up yet!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Don't give up yet!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: I'm here with you. Let's keep going!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: I'm here with you. Let's keep going!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Where does her strength come from?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Where does her strength come from?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: She fights like a woman possessed.{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: She fights like a woman possessed.{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: She's no woman... She's a demon!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: She's no woman... She's a demon!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: She'd be super hot if she wasn't trying to kill us...{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: She'd be super hot if she wasn't trying to kill us...{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: No kidding. What a shame!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: No kidding. What a shame!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Where's the dragon?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Where's the dragon?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Nowhere to be found.{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Nowhere to be found.{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: I'm ready to do this!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: I'm ready to do this!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: She...she's made it this far...?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: She...she's made it this far...?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: This ends here!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: This ends here!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Where did her dragon go!?{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Where did her dragon go!?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: She's coming this way!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: She's coming this way!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Lady Five! Protect me!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Lady Five! Protect me!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Savage girl! You'll have to strike this old man down first!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Savage girl! You'll have to strike this old man down first!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: I'm not afraid... I'm not afraid!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: I'm not afraid... I'm not afraid!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: 目標達成　敵兵士を撃破した！{#Name="説明文"}
source: 目標達成　敵兵士を撃破した！{#Name="説明文"}

translation: こんな所に閉じ込めやがって……{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: こんな所に閉じ込めやがって……{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ふっ……ふふふっ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: ふっ……ふふふっ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ゼロ！？どうしたの？大丈夫！？{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: ゼロ！？どうしたの？大丈夫！？{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: いや、逆に楽しくなってきたよ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: いや、逆に楽しくなってきたよ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 楽しい？どうして？{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: 楽しい？どうして？{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: これだけ鬱陶しい想いをさせてもらったんだ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: これだけ鬱陶しい想いをさせてもらったんだ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 後から{LF}ファイブをブチ殺す楽しみが増えてしょうがないよ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 後から{LF}ファイブをブチ殺す楽しみが増えてしょうがないよ{#Name="ゼロ"}

source: うん！楽しいのがふえるのはいいことだね！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: Aaaaaah!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Aaaaaah!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Look out! Friendly fire!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Look out! Friendly fire!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Hold your ground! For Lady Five's sake!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Hold your ground! For Lady Five's sake!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Well, aren't you the brave one?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Well, aren't you the brave one?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: That cannon fire's annoying, though.{LF}Better keep moving.{#Name="Zero"}
source: That cannon fire's annoying, though.{LF}Better keep moving.{#Name="Zero"}
